	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Here's how to view them</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In order to see this document, follow these directions.
<br />
<br />1. go to <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.ipdl.jpo.go.jp/homepg_e.ipdl">http://www.ipdl.jpo.go.jp/homepg_e.ipdl</a><!-- m -->
<br />2. click on Patent &amp; Utility Model Gazette DB
<br />3. Enter Kind Code: A
<br />4. Enter Number: S55-096186
<br />5. click on search, a link to document JP,55-096186,A(1980) will appear in a pane on the left.  click it
<br />6. You will be told that the document is not available in English, so Click on the button that says JAPANESE.
<br />
<br />If anyone can make sense of it, please post the info on these boards.  The pictures themselves are somewhat revealing, even with the japanese captions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


