	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Easy - the Famicom version used the Konami VRC6, which had 3 extra sound channels. The NES does not support expansion sound, so the music had to be rewritten using only the internal sound channels.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


